thread.title: VOL
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by VOL

author: VOL
title: VOL
text:
The car I rent was a Nissan Tilda, not a new one but comfortable and I drived more than 5 000 km in 4 weeks very safely from Queenstown to Auckland , with the same car.
The welcomings at the beginning and return were very friendly.
I recommend strongly this car rental !
